lf. “The day after tomorrow! Sehr gut. What a state my shoes are in! Mary will be amazed. Still, we’ll survive somehow. We’ll rent a nice cheap little flat. She’ll decide. Meanwhile we’ll live here for a bit. Thank goodness there’s a door between the two rooms.”

A short while later he went out into the passage and knocked at his neighbor’s.

Ganin thought, “Why can’t they leave me alone today?”

